Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:10.99,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:37.45,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun considers \Nthe Clover Kingdom their enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:42.93,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Their goal is to defeat the Clover Kingdom \Nand create their own independent nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:45.64,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They believe that once they \Ngather all the magic stones,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:49.86,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,they will transform into their true \Nforms and inherit great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.28,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But in order for them to \Nattain their true forms,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:54.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,they need three more magic stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:58.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It was discovered that one of those \Nstones lies in the Underwater Temple,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:01.89,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,within a strong magic region.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:03.54,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:04.75,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:39.62,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,480)}A Black Beach Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:40.79,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to complete our \Nmission yet again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:45.54,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure our great Captain \NVangeance will praise us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:46.61,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:47.59,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:48.39,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:54.40,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Sylph, was it? Your spirit \Nmagic is indeed powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:58.44,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to stop fighting on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.49,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We are a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:03.66,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno is ignoring him brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:11.24,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? Next time, don't ignore my orders \Nand defeat all of the enemies instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.88,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We will do things according to my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.36,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.75,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.05,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:20.42,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.86,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I think it came from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.18,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's an incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.26,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:28.92,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:30.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.10,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:31.94,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,A robbery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.69,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:40.65,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:46.87,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Swimsuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.40,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, little Golden Dawn boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:50.20,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.18,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the ocean tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:57.20,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle doesn't have a swimsuit, \Nso I was helping her pick one out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:04:01.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I even told her she could borrow one \Nof mine, but she doesn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It was just strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.18,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How could I possibly wear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.95,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:11.18,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Then that scream earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:14.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's because Vanessa \Nsuddenly took off my clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:18.68,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it makes no sense to try on \Nswimsuits while still wearing clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:21.19,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own fault for \Ntaking forever to undress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.26,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.32,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.20,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What about this one, Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:29.14,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, there's no way I could wear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.58,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,All this fuss over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.90,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Picking out swimsuits to go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.88,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lot just fooling \Naround instead of working again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.16,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! This is for a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:42.31,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,A mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:43.57,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:47.72,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,An s-e-c-r-e-t one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.43,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come along, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.39,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,How adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.85,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any spare time \Non our hands, so I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:05:02.86,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to go to the beach, but we\Nalso have another mission tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.11,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:08.74,italics,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's my Meal-Saving Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:09.35,top,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I would've loved to see you \Nin a swimsuit, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.07,top,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:13.00,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he'll say if \Nhe sees me in my swimsuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:13.00,top,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you pics later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:18.50,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Glance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:23.17,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,She's so sexy! She looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:24.97,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:27.73,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm flattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.47,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Devour me—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.18,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.22,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Owie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:38.02,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's my Meal-Saving Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:41.01,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Dawn kids already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:42.90,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.37,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you've already \Npicked out your swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.86,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just need you to hurry \Nup and pick one, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.57,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:52.41,main,noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I can't wear that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.45,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this one over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:55.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Over where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.54,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little expensive, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:02.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The price doesn't matter. \NIt's pretty and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:06.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But... it doesn't seem to cover very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:09.39,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Also, what's all that flashy decoration for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:12.47,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,All eyes will be on you at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.02,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:17.98,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Stupidsta will notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.79,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he'll at least\Ncompliment me if I wear this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:25.86,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care if he notices me or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.65,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What would you like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.28,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy it, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:33.92,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:34.86,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:39.75,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, you bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:47.42,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,My goddess Marie... I wanted \Nto take you to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:50.34,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if whales are stronger than sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.26,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Sharks have very rough skin.\NDid you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:07:01.02,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you two on my Crazy Cyclone, \Ntotally expecting a ride from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I can't fly on a broom, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for me. Did you already forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:08.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.12,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.66,main,Manga,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you guys ride \Non someone else's broom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You have royalty like me\Noffering to ride with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.20,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You should be thankful, you peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:22.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is Captain Yami still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:25.68,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted to check \Nsomething out and left earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:30.59,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Really? It's pretty unusual for \Nhim to actually do some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.18,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mr. Yami for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.93,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:41.94,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Crazy Cyclone, blast off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:52.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The place where Asta and the others are \Nheaded is an oceanfront town called Raquey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:57.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Raquey has very strong mana, \Ncausing it to be hot year-round.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:08:02.00,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This makes it a popular resort getaway \Nfor royalty, nobles, and Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:07.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you just use your spatial \Nmagic to get there, Finral?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.07,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been to Raquey before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:13.76,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use my spatial magic to go \Nto places I haven't been to before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.71,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Tch. You're so useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:18.89,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Now we have to fly over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:21.14,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I have seniority over you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.21,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you've never \Nbeen there before, Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:28.04,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you were flirting with \Nall the girls on the beach there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:33.68,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's always better to save \Nthe best things for last.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.99,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I haven't gone yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:40.24,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited to go to Raquey!\NWait for me, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:44.29,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait. The guy who's always \Nawkwardly exhaling steam isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.29,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.53,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So wait, that was Grey?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:09:00.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then where's the real Gordon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:04.23,sign_12963_144_Huh__Guys__Are_y,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Guys? Are you still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:06.31,sign_13058_146_Isn_t_it_time_to,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it time to leave soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:11.94,sign_12963_144_Huh__Guys__Are_y,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Did they already leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:16.68,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to see it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.34,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:23.04,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait! I've never seen it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Me, neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:30.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But I still don't see any sign of it. \NIs Raquey still pretty far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.84,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,No, it shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.50,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:37.80,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We've been looking at the \Nocean for quite some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.27,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:44.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's so huge, I couldn't even tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:46.52,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,It's beyond my wildest dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.77,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the ocean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:07.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean... It's so huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:11.08,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome... This is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:14.25,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could show Yuno and \Nthe other runts this view, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.61,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:18.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And someday, I'd love to \Nbring Sister Lily here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.55,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.26,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,The sunset's so beautiful, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:28.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... But Sister Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're even more beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.31,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I became the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh! Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:41.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.17,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:48.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.25,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's he smirking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:56.84,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He'd better not be remembering that k-k-kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:11:00.29,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wipe that smirk off your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:04.14,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It's not like I'd ever \Nkiss him or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:12.51,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show off this swimsuit \NI bought yesterday in front of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:14.92,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:20.03,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to show him that \NI'm way better than Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.66,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:31.53,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But I want him to see me... \NBut this is still really embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.37,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:41.63,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Stupidsta! Wh-What do you \Nthink about this swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:45.00,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like my awesome swimwear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What the heck is that, Magna?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:53.52,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it awesome?! This is something that \NMr. Yami also uses! It's called a loincloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:54.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Dork.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:59.96,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Let's swim to our hearts' content in this \Nocean that's as big as Mr. Yami's heart, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:02.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.53,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:08.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of my swimsuit? \NDoesn't it look great on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:11.43,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that different from \Nhow you usually dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:15.88,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I guess a virgin delinquent like you \Ncan't understand adult charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:18.14,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a virgin delinquent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.09,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go for a run?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:24.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're on fire, Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:30.50,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you blasted fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:34.23,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Marie?\N I made it look just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:36.53,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.90,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brother, show me the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.90,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. With pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:44.53,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Marie. This is the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:48.03,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! It's so big and beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:52.20,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we can come here \Ntogether and splash around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's pretty cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:13:00.84,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Asta! I want to play \Nwith Asta in the ocean someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:04.21,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:06.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving you permission to \Nlook at me in my swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:09.30,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who tries to tempt my Marie shall die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.64,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.31,top,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic: Reflect Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:14.99,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:20.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's so salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:22.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, huh?! I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.58,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:25.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, look at me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.03,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:34.08,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,So, so many hot girls in swimsuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:37.62,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go flirting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:40.29,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Grey! Transform into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.96,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Check it out, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:49.50,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Grey! We'll be twins, and our selling \Npoint can be our snappy dialogue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:50.32,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.30,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:55.73,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,This goes hand-in-hand with the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.48,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,If it's food, I know it \Nlike the back of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.77,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:05.05,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats having drinks on the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:08.42,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Charmy, you need to move more to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.28,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:12.25,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you helping Finral \Npick up some girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:16.95,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I got bored, so I left him behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:19.16,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,A little more to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:20.43,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:21.70,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:24.94,italics,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell... Just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.30,italics,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Just... ten more steps!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:32.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.23,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Asta, my swimsuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:36.56,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,You're right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:39.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:41.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Miz Charmy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If you had hit anyone else, they'd be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:45.73,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, watermelon juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:49.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! My swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:56.23,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Asta. It only occurred to me after I \Nturned into you, but your muscles are gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:15:00.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You should use your transformation \Nspell for something more useful, Grey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're wasting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:03.21,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,My swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:04.71,main,asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:12.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like I thought! Running on this \Nsand is excellent training for my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:18.91,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me in my swimsuit, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:25.23,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't control your magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:27.40,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You saved my butt this time, but seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.40,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, it went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:32.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. All I can manage without a staff are \Ndefense spells that remain stationary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.57,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you bragging about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:44.25,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:45.79,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:49.13,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the famous Raquey Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:51.80,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean is calling my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:54.28,main,Budede,0000,0000,0000,,Sekke, should we really be playing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.35,main,Afuafu,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that all we really do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:59.43,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did such a good \Njob on that last mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:02.68,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,that the Wizard King gave me a hundred stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:06.36,sign_23006_275___Lies__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,< Lies >
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:03.96,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.89,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Jack praised me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:11.49,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,And most importantly, I saved all \Nthe kids from those evildoers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:14.72,sign_23280_279___This_Is_Somewh,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,750)}< This Is Somewhat True >
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:15.05,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't hurt for me \Nto spread my wings a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.74,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, beautiful ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:18.17,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:19.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:20.92,main,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:24.30,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see. Want to come play with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:25.54,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.34,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.96,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.62,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:31.30,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that loser trying to pick up girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.50,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, you two. Go pick up some girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.26,main,Budede,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What about you, Sekke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:40.71,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid bah-hastard!\NI can't do something so vulgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:44.02,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'll meet up with you guys after you \Nsuccessfully pick up some girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:50.48,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,This jerk! He's planning to show up \Nand act like he's doing us a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:55.64,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason you got to come here is \Nbecause of me, the Magic Knight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:59.62,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you a chance. Now, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.76,main,Budede,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:03.16,main,Afuafu,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:09.88,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there are some ideal \Nbabes right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:13.70,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Don't worry about me! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:16.22,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,You go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:21.14,main,Budede,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, cuties!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:25.02,main,Afuafu,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come talk with us about \Nhow awesome magical girls are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.11,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:31.55,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,She's from the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:34.82,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, does that also mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:40.08,top,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, damn it! Explosive Scattershot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.57,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:39.16,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hup! Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:40.08,top,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Die! Reflect Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.54,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.88,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:52.50,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.43,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Did we just run something over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:55.23,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:57.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I think we ran into something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.77,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Nyom, nyom, nyom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:04.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hey! We came here to \Nlook for the magic stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:07.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you all playing around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:08.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And you're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:10.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Yami...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:15.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, gather round, you idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:18.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I picked up some info while \Nyou were messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:19.94,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:24.08,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the Underwater Temple\Nreally is at the bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:28.19,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But the mana kicks up the \Nocean currents so much that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:31.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,ordinarily, even a first-class \Nmage can't get near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:34.37,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But on the night of the full moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:37.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,the mana becomes weaker.\NWe might be able to get in then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:42.22,italics,All,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Yami is actually, \Nseriously doing his job!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seriously going to murder all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:46.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:50.92,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Like the name suggests, the Underwater \NTemple is on the ocean floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:53.00,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just walk to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:54.92,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So Noelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:58.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Take us there with your water magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:18:59.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:00.91,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a ride there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:06.66,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I'd need incredible magic \Ncontrol in order to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.54,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! You should ask someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:13.55,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean, if I fail...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:14.63,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:18.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you fail, the fierce currents will \Ntake us all under, and we'll drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:24.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This is a top secret mission \Nentrusted to only the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,No one else can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.10,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:31.10,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The next full moon is a week away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:34.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Learn to control it by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:36.61,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Surpass your limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:50.97,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Dragon's Lair... Right now,\Nit's my only spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:54.25,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Developing it further should \Nbe the quickest way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.21,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:09.81,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa taught me some magic control\Ntricks before, but none of them have worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:14.44,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I just don't have the \Nability to control magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:25.34,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I don't have talent, \NI won't run or make excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:28.12,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just keep working... \Nuntil I figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:32.89,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:36.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.48,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So you were training too, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:41.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And you too, Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.93,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-As if a royal like me would train.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's train together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:48.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:52.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose control again, \NI'll be able to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:56.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hmph! That won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:59.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Training with just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:05.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, if you insist,\NI guess I wouldn't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:07.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:08.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I hear something.
