Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:22:59.33,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:03.77,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Look at Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:02.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.25,0:23:07.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Stupidsta. Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:10.28,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look in this swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:17.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're all sparkly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:18.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.78,0:23:21.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That'd probably work great\Nas part of a scarecrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:25.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You sort of look like a cow back in Hage...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:29.80,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you staring at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:27.24,main,Crab,0000,0000,0000,,Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:29.80,main,Crab,0000,0000,0000,,Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:33.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But you told me to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:34.93,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, I'm so embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:37.45,main,Crab,0000,0000,0000,,Crab...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:44.92,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Did you all enjoy yet another \Nappearance by me, the great Sekke Bronzazza?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:47.65,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm even more bah-hawesome on the beach!
